  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nIn Process Explorer, child processes of chrome do not have Untrusted Integrity level. Instead, now they have Low Integrity. It persists after restarting process explorer, and I could set the Integrity Level to Untrusted, which showed updated Integrity Level (Untrusted)."
